dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data set shows the boundaries of public water utility districts in Snohomish County. This data is not a comprehensive coverage of all Water Districts in Snohomish County. The data depicts only those districts which hold elections. It is one of several districts maintained by the Auditor's Office. District bounaries are registered with the Integrated Land Records (ILR) parcel data set, with some exceptions.
